{{Youmay|the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic's]] [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Senate]] committee on [[Refugee/Legends|refugees]]|the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[Senate Select Committee for Refugees]]|linebreak=1}}
The '''Senate Committee on Refugees''' met to discuss the withdrawal of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] [[Garrison/Legends|garrison]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Qiilura/Legends|Qiilura]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

[[General/Legends|General]] [[Arligan Zey]] met with General [[Iri Camas]] and the chair of the committee on the 385th day after the [[First Battle of Geonosis/Legends|First Battle of Geonosis]] in response to the potential threat posed by the native [[Gurlanin]]s in them turning against the Republic after it was discovered by [[Omega Squad]] that some of these aliens had infiltrated [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Zey commented that such a withdrawal both served the interest of the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] and was inevitable anyway, given how thinly stretched the Republic forces were at that time.

